00:55:28.736 --> 00:55:36.257
Specifically, we are using that input to change the subset of our data set.

00:55:36.257 --> 00:55:41.257
So what I like to do, especially when you're starting out, is, yes, save the variable of

00:55:41.257 --> 00:55:45.936
the input that you're using, called species, and then passing it back in right here.

00:55:45.936 --> 00:55:52.297
