This return type is tips filtered, but the function is called filter underscore data.

02:17:08.710 --> 02:17:16.549
So that means that any time I want to use this reactive filter data set, I call filtered

02:17:16.549 --> 02:17:18.070
underscore data.

02:17:18.070 --> 02:17:25.749
And so right here, where this all became index one, index two, intersect, return, I can just

02:17:25.749 --> 02:17:32.510
say just take that data set, give me the first value of the shape, which is the number of

02:17:32.510 --> 02:17:33.510
rows.

